    Paralysis, Aerostreak, Guantix, Grappler, Adrax, and Autofire return to 
base after the assult. Getting closer they see Scorpinox standing in front of 
the base. What a perfect oppertunity for target practice.
    "I suggest you surrender! Your outnumbered and if you try to run we will 
kill you!" Paralysis said, loading his gun.

    In the engine room she began to construction project that would free her 
mind of Tarantulas. The lowhalf of his body was complete, the upper half 
would take longer. It was very complex and in much smaller peices. She 
shighed and went back to work. The sooner Aracnia had him out of her head, 
the better.
